  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You throw two held weapons at the target, one directly behind the other, at your highest attack bonus. If the first one hits, the target will be denied its Dexterity bonus to Defense against the second attack. If the first attack missed, the target may choose to make a Reflex save against your attack roll instead of using its Defense.<br><br>The weapons have a range increment of 10 ft, and deal normal damage when they hit. Each weapon that hit will fall to the ground in the target's square, while each weapon that missed falls to the ground 10 ft behind it.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to retrieve the weapon(s) by moving to a square adjacent to the thrown weapon(s) and making an attack roll against a Defense of 15. This can only be done if you benefit from Speed Rank 1 or higher. This is a move action.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
